choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.
Okay, I've put together a balanced and nutritious meal plan for you for today! Breakfast: 1 cup of oatmeal with half a banana and some almonds. Lunch: A salad made up of romaine lettuce, chicken breast, tomatoes, carrots, and a light dressing. Dinner: Baked salmon served over brown rice, steamed broccoli on the side. Snacks: An apple with peanut butter or some Greek yogurt with berries.
Is that all you eat for one day?
